 Market price corrections.\n\nRTM Price Corrections\n\nReal-Time Market price corrections  ...    ## Real-Time Prices Reports\n\nLMPs by Electrical Bus View the Locational Marginal Price for each Electrical Bus, normally produced by SCED every five minutes. LMPs by Resource Nodes, Load Zones and Trading Hubs View the Locational Marginal Price for each Settlement Point, normally produced by SCED every five minutes. RTD Indicative LMPs by Resource Nodes, Load Zones and Hubs This report is posted after every Look Ahead RTD run and includes indicative LMPs at Resource Nodes, Hub LMPs and Load  ...    Settlement Point Prices at Resource Nodes, Hubs and Load Zones View the Settlement Point Price for each Settlement Point, produced from SCED LMPs every 15 minutes. ##### Related Content\n\n###### On this site - Business Practice Manual\n- [Real"
